&gt; &gt; you just need to keep your eyes open and look for them.<br />
&gt; &gt;</font><br />
&gt;<br />
&gt; I disagree. Solo monsters rarely drop chests which is why solo quests</font><br />
are<font color="#7F7FFF"><br />
&gt; desperately needed for the solo player.</font><br />
<br />
Rarely compared to groups, yes.  But my feeling is that it is about 1/5<br />
to 1/6 as rare, which is about the same for one person to score<br />
something from a group dropped chest.  I worked on my disarm by soloing<br />
green and blue orcs because the chests dropped often enough that I<br />
wouldn't have to risk killing any groups trying to work on that skill.<br />
<br />
