Timothy is talking about Everquest, you are talking about Everquest 2.<br />
I think this will lead to confusion...<br />
<br />
Anyway, if you want to improve your character, there are lots of<br />
crafters who will be happy to sell you equipment, as well as groupers<br />
who have gotten nice drops they don't need.  As a soloer you will<br />
never get as good equipment as someone who groups, but in my<br />
experience the big money is to be made from harvesting and selling the<br />
results, which is a solo endeavour, so it should be possible to do<br />
fairly well.<br />
<br />
<font color="#7F7FFF"><br />
&gt; Also the lack of solo quests at higher levels also forces people to group as<br />
&gt; there's no other way of ganing experience.</font><br />
